      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### SLO Dashboard - luong ra tien (browse -> cart -> checkout)\nNguon: **spanmetrics** (`traces_span_metrics_*`). Success = span khong `STATUS_CODE_ERROR`. Cua so live 5m; error budget 24h. Nguong: checkout >=99%, browse/cart >=99.5%, storefront p95 <1s."
      }
    },
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 2 },
      "id": 101,
      "type": "row",
      "collapsed": false,
      "title": "SLO hien tai (rolling 5m)",
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "webstore-metrics" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 3 },
      "id": 1,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Checkout success rate (SLO >= 99%)",
      "description": "Ty le span checkout khong loi. Nguong 99% (revenue-critical).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "min": 90,
          "max": 100,
          "decimals": 2,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "green", "value": 99 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "webstore-metrics" },
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "100 * sum(rate(traces_span_metrics_calls_total{service_name=\"checkout\",status_code!=\"STATUS_CODE_ERROR\"}[5m])) / clamp_min(sum(rate(traces_span_metrics_calls_total{service_name=\"checkout\"}[5m])), 1e-9)"
        }
      ]
    },
